# Binary Tree Class
A simple binary tree class in Python, developed for educational purposes only.

# Features
- Supports Multiple Traversal Orders: { Pre-Order, In-Order, Post-Order }
- Recursive Search Method
- Minimal, Simplistic Design

# Usage Example (Python)
from binary_tree import TreeNode
root = TreeNode( 2, TreeNode(1), TreeNode(3) )
root.output("in")  # Prints: 1 2 3
print( root.search(3) )  # Prints: True
